OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with some
OL,6,Fbright or sunny intervals and showers.
OL,7,FShowers may be heavy and merge to give
OL,8,Flonger spells of rain. Becoming drier
OL,9,Ffrom the west later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers slowly dying out
OL,12,Fthrough the evening. Dry with clear
OL,13,Fspells in the east overnight but
OL,14,Fturning cloudy with further showers
OL,15,Fspreading into Dumfries and Galloway.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA dry and bright start in
OL,18,Fthe east. Otherwise rather cloudy with
OL,19,Fshowers, some heavy and thundery, but
OL,20,Fbecoming drier in the west later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
